  sequenceId: DAY4_OPENING_SCENE
  sequenceTitle: Day4_Opening
  description: "Cu\u1ED1i ng\xE0y 3, sinh vi\xEAn trao \u0111\u1ED5i qu\u1ED1c t\u1EBF
    xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 c\u1EA7u n\u1ED1i sang ng\xE0y 4."
  defaultCharacterInterval: 0.025
  hideAfterFinished: 1
  lines:
  - speakerName: 
    showAvatar: 0
    avatar: {fileID: 0}
    content: "Cu\u1ED1i ng\xE0y, khi V\u0169 \u0111ang chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB d\u1ECDn
      c\u1ED5ng, m\u1ED9t sinh vi\xEAn l\u1EA1 m\u1EB7t xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n tr\u01B0\u1EDBc
      C7."
